a good companion.

410
00:24:27,568 --> 00:24:28,936
I like you.

411
00:24:28,970 --> 00:24:30,805
You're the only person who has
ever shown me kindness

412
00:24:30,838 --> 00:24:32,707
in my entire life.

413
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:35,509
Well,
I'm sorry to hear that.

414
00:24:42,817 --> 00:24:44,118
