in Ingolstadt,

474
00:28:01,115 --> 00:28:03,918
but most of my life
was spent in Switzerland.

475
00:28:03,951 --> 00:28:06,320
An orphan?

476
00:28:06,353 --> 00:28:08,022
Abandoned.

477
00:28:08,055 --> 00:28:10,891
